'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tPercent yield<br />\n\tPercent yield means the amount of actual product as a ratio to the theoretical amount of product. What is the percentage yield referring to? Is the percentage yield low or high?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They calculated the percentage yield... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) calculating the percent yield in an experiment<br />\n\t2) maximizing the percent yield<br />\n\t3) percentage yield inconsistent<br />\n\t4) modifying the percentage yield<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tAlthough the overall yield might be lower, the percentage yield of the intended catch would be much greater. This trap setting method was thus more sustainable than sea floor scraping since the habitat was much less disturbed that way. It was important for people to be aware of the concept of sustainability. In terms of food choices people made, if everyone was more aware of how the food on their plates came to be, not only would it be more healthy for their bodies, the environment would be in a much better place as well.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/166651637810/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p764490/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p764490\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p765617/\">卡梅伦猴年新春贺词 附语言点精炼</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p762647/\">摄影师：有个拍照爱挡脸的女友是怎样的体验</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764412/\">每周词汇精选：Native</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p577813/\">过年大吐槽：我为什么害怕过春节？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p761787/\">前台心里苦：盘点住店旅客奇葩问题TOP10</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p270163/\">与老外话春节：中国餐桌礼仪和传统习惯</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p765637/\">酷玩乐队携手碧昂斯火星哥引爆超级碗中场秀</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p762205/\">新发明 不再被音乐叫醒 气味闹钟每天香醒你</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p762893/\">新年要幸福！杜克大学的13堂幸福课（有声）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p161331/\">新概念英语第一册Lesson 1  Excuse me</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http: